            <title>【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼鏡加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼鏡開會即總結會議要點</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=oppo-air-glasses</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:53:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[oppo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[OPPO Air Glass 3 XR]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221787</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OPPO 近日在世界流動通訊大會（Mobile World Congress，MWC）發布全新「輔助實境智能眼鏡」OPPO Air Glass 3 概念產品，據官方資料顯示，OPPO Air Glass 3 能夠利用手機專屬 App 使用 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/img02.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3，圖片來源：OPPO</p><p>OPPO 表示，Air Glass 3 XR 現階段屬概念產品，重量僅在 50g 左右，採用 OPPO 自主研發的樹脂晶圓衍射光波導鏡片，折射率高達 1.70，顯示亮度均勻性大於 50%，入眼峯值亮度超過 1000 尼特。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO 示範影片可見， Air Glass 3 XR 能顯示不少資訊</p><p>OPPO 官方表示，使用者可利用手機裏的 OPPO Air Glass 3 專屬應用程式，開啟旗下自主研發的 AI 大模型 AndesGPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 專屬應用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲輕觸眼鏡的鏡臂就能夠使用語音助理功能</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/oppoairglass3concept-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲OPPO Air Glass 3 XR 實際佩戴</p><p style="text-align: left;">雖然 OPPO 這款 XR 眼鏡看起來非常高科技，而且官方示範影片裏面出現的功能亦很實用，OPPO 方面尚未透露 Air Glass 3 XR 上市時間表，因此就讓我們拭目以待吧。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51149"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SedimxtA73g?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: left;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.oppo.com/cn/newsroom/press/514/">OPPO</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SedimxtA73g">Oppo@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/06/oppo-find-n3-flip-review/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】OPPO Find N3 Flip　外形　手感　鉸位　功能　屏幕　相機　效能開箱評測</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/28/nokia-and-oppo-sign-crosslicense-5g-patent-agreement/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">OPPO 與 Nokia 簽訂專利交叉授權，終止長達兩年訴訟戰</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/oppo-air-glasses/vr-mr-ar/">【MWC 2024】OPPO Air Glass 3 智能眼鏡加入 AI「AndesGPT」    戴眼鏡開會即總結會議要點</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
